  "A·B = |A||B|cos(θ) = 0 implies cos(θ) = 0, so θ = 90°. The vectors are perpendicular (orthogonal).": "AB = ABCos( ) = 0 表示 cos( ) = 0, so  = 90 °。 矢量是垂直的( 垂直的) 。",
  "A displacement vector is 50 m at 37° north of east. What are the east and north components?": "东纬37度以北50米处为迁移矢量,东面和北面有哪些组成部分?",
