  "East component = 50 cos37° ≈ 50(0.8) = 40 m. North component = 50 sin37° ≈ 50(0.6) = 30 m.": "东部分 = 50 cos37° = 50(0.8) = 40 m. 北部分 = 50 sin37° = 50(0.6) = 30 m.",
  "What is 2A - B if A = (1, 3) and B = (4, -2)?": "如果A=(1,3)和B=(4,2),2A-B是什么?",
