  "2A - B = 2(1,3) - (4,-2) = (2,6) - (4,-2) = (2-4, 6-(-2)) = (-2, 8).": "2A - B = 21,3) - (4,2) = 2,6) - (4,2) - (4,2) = 2,4,6-(2) = (2,8) = 2,4,6-(2) = (2,8) 。",
  "Three forces act on an object: F₁ = 10 N east, F₂ = 10 N north, F₃ = 10 N at 45° south of west. What is the approximate magnitude of the resultant?": "F1 = 东经10牛顿,F2 = 北经10牛顿,F3 = 东经45度以南的10牛顿。",
  "20 N": "20 N",
