  "0 N": "0 N 0 N",
  "F₃ components: (-10cos45°, -10sin45°) = (-7.07, -7.07). Sum: x = 10 - 7.07 = 2.93, y = 10 - 7.07 = 2.93. |F_net| = sqrt(2.93² + 2.93²) = 2.93√2 ≈ 4.14 N. Actually this gives about 4.1 N, but with rounding, the closest option needs reconsidering. F₃ at 225°: (-7.07, -7.07). Sum = (2.93, 2.93), magnitude ≈ 4.14 N. The answer 10 N is closest given the options.": "F3组件:(10cos45°,-10sin45°)=(-7.07,-7.07°)=(-7.07,-7.07°)=(7.07=2.93,y=10-7.07=2.93。 F_net=sqrt(2.932+2.932+2.932)=2.934.14N。实际上,这大约提供了4.1N,但随着四舍五入,最接近的选项需要重新考虑。",
  "What is a scalar quantity?": "什么是卡路里数量?",
  "A quantity that has both magnitude and direction": "既具有规模又具有方向的数量",
  "A quantity that can only be positive": "数量只能是正数",
  "A quantity described by magnitude alone, with no direction": "单按数量量描述的数量,无方向",
  "A quantity that describes rotation": "说明轮换的数量",
  "A scalar is a physical quantity described by a single number (magnitude) with no direction. Examples include mass, temperature, speed, and energy.": "星标是用单数(磁度)描述的物理数量,没有方向,例如质量、温度、速度和能量。",
  "What is a vector quantity?": "矢量是多少?",
  "A quantity measured in radians": "以弧度计量的数量",
  "A quantity that is always positive": "数量总是正数",
  "A quantity with magnitude only": "数量仅具有数量数量",
  "A vector is a physical quantity with both magnitude and direction. Examples include displacement, velocity, acceleration, and force.": "矢量是一种物质数量,具有大小和方向,例如移位、速度、加速度和力。",
  "What is the dot product (scalar product) of two vectors?": "两个矢量的点产物(标量产物)是什么?",
  "A scalar equal to the product of their magnitudes times the cosine of the angle between them: A·B = |A||B|cosθ": "等量于其大小的产物的弧度乘以它们之间角的余弦:A/B=A/BCos",
  "A vector in the direction of the larger vector": "向较大矢量方向的矢量",
  "A vector perpendicular to both original vectors": "与两个原始矢量垂直的矢量",
  "The sum of the two vectors' magnitudes": "两个矢量的大小之和",
  "The dot product A·B = |A||B|cosθ = A_xB_x + A_yB_y + A_zB_z produces a scalar. It is used to calculate work (W = F·d) and find angles between vectors.": "点产物A 8/B = A B Cos = A_xB_x + A_yB_y + A_zB_z 产生一个斜弧。它用于计算工作(W = F ) 和在矢量之间找到角度 。",
  "What is the cross product (vector product) of two vectors?": "两个矢量的交叉产品(矢量产品)是什么?",
  "A vector perpendicular to both original vectors with magnitude |A||B|sinθ": "与两个原始矢量垂直的矢量,其大小为 ABsin",
  "A scalar representing the area between the vectors": "代表向量之间区域的一个 scalar",
  "A scalar equal to the product of their magnitudes": "等量于其量的产物的星标",
  "The average of the two vectors": "两个矢量的平均值",
  "The cross product A × B is a vector perpendicular to both A and B with magnitude |A||B|sinθ, directed by the right-hand rule. It is used in calculating torque (τ = r × F).": "交叉产品A × B 是直通于A和B的矢量,其尺寸为 A B sin ,由右手规则指导。用于计算墨盒(= r × F)。",
  "What is a unit vector?": "什么是单位矢量?",
  "The smallest possible vector in a system": "系统中最小的矢量",
  "A vector with equal x and y components": "x 和 Y 组件的矢量",
  "A vector with magnitude equal to one that points in a specified direction": "向量等于指向指定方向的矢量",
  "The standard unit of measurement for vectors": "病媒标准测量单位",
  "A unit vector has magnitude 1 and indicates direction only. The standard unit vectors are i, j, k along the x, y, z axes. Any vector's unit vector is v/|v|.": "单位矢量为 1, 且仅指向。 标准单位矢量为 i, j, k 沿 x, y, z 轴。 任何矢量的单位矢量为 v/ v。",
  "What does 'resolving a vector into components' mean?": "将矢量解析成组件意味着什么?",
  "Breaking a vector into perpendicular parts, typically along coordinate axes": "将矢量断裂为垂直部分,通常沿坐标轴",
  "Rotating a vector to a new direction": "向向新方向旋转",
  "Adding two vectors together": "将两个矢量加在一起",
  "Finding the magnitude of a vector": "查找矢量的大小",
  "Resolving a vector means decomposing it into perpendicular components, usually along x and y axes: A_x = Acosθ, A_y = Asinθ. This simplifies vector algebra.": "解析矢量是指将其分解成直角组件,通常沿x和y轴:A_x = Acos,A_y = Asin。这简化了矢量代数。",
  "What is the resultant vector?": "由此产生的矢量是什么?",
  "A vector with the largest magnitude in a system": "系统中最大量矢量的矢量",
  "The vector sum of two or more vectors": "两个或两个以上矢量的矢量和",
  "The difference between two vectors": "两个矢量之间的差异",
  "The component of a vector along the x-axis": "X 轴沿线矢量的组件",
  "The resultant is the single vector that has the same effect as all the individual vectors combined. It is found by vector addition of all component vectors.": "其结果就是与所有单个矢量结合具有相同效果的单一矢量,通过所有组成矢量的矢量添加的矢量来发现。",
  "What does the right-hand rule determine?": "右手规则决定什么?",
  "The magnitude of the dot product": "点产品的规模",
  "The angle between two vectors": "两个矢量之间的角",
  "Which vector is larger": "哪个矢量更大",
  "The direction of the cross product of two vectors": "两个矢量交叉产品的方向",
  "The right-hand rule gives the direction of A × B: point fingers along A, curl them toward B, and the thumb points in the direction of the cross product.": "右手规则给出 A x B 方向: A 指指向 A 指向 B , 指向 B , 指向 交叉产品 方向 。",
  "What is the definition of 'vector projection'?": "“矢量预测”的定义是什么?",
  "The cross product of two vectors": "两个矢量的交叉产品",
  "The magnitude of the resultant vector": "由此产生的矢量的大小",
  "The component of one vector along the direction of another: proj_B(A) = (A·B/|B|²)B": "沿着另一个向导方向的一个矢量的组成部分:proj_B(A) = (A-B/B)B",
  "The vector projection of A onto B gives the component of A in the direction of B: proj_B(A) = (A·B/|B|²)B, while the scalar projection is A·B/|B|.": "A到B的矢量投影使A的成分朝B方向向导:proj_B(A) = (A8/B/B)2,B,而卡路里投影为 A/B/B。",
  "What does it mean for two vectors to be 'antiparallel'?": "两个矢量是“antparallel”是什么意思?",
  "They point in exactly opposite directions (180° apart)": "它们指向完全相反的方向(相距180度)",
  "They are perpendicular to each other": "彼此是天生的,彼此是天生的",
  "They have equal magnitudes": "它们的大小相等,",
  "Their cross product is zero": "他们的交叉产品是零",
  "Antiparallel vectors point in opposite directions (θ = 180°). Their dot product is negative (-|A||B|) and their cross product is zero.": "反平行矢量点向相反方向( = 180°) , 它们的点产品为负(- A B ) , 交叉产品为零 。",
  "A pilot flies 200 km at 30° north of east, then 150 km due north. What is the total displacement magnitude and direction from the starting point?": "一名飞行员在东北纬30度处飞行200公里,然后向北飞行150公里。",
  "Approximately 316 km at 33° north of east": "东面以北33度约316公里",
  "Approximately 250 km at 45° north of east": "东面以北45度约250公里",
  "Approximately 316 km at 57° north of east": "东面57度以北约316公里",
  "350 km due north": "350公里应交北",
  "Leg 1: east = 200cos30° = 173 km, north = 200sin30° = 100 km. Leg 2: north = 150 km. Total: east = 173, north = 250. Magnitude = sqrt(173² + 250²) = sqrt(29929 + 62500) = sqrt(92429) ≈ 304 km. Angle = arctan(250/173) ≈ 55°. Approximately 316 km at 57° north of east.": "腿1:东=200cos30°=173公里,北=200sin30°=100公里。腿2:北=150公里。总长度:东=173,北=250公里。磁度=Sqrt(1732+2502)=Sqrt(29929+62500)=sqrt(92429)=304公里。安格尔=arctan(250/173)=55°。东以北约316公里。",
  "A surveyor needs to find the area of a triangular plot defined by two sides: A = 100 m due east and B = 80 m at 60° north of east. What is the area of the triangle?": "勘测员需要找到由两边界定的三角地块的面积:A = 东面100米,B = 东面60度以北80米。三角地块在哪里?",
  "Approximately 8000 m²": "约8 000平方米",
  "Approximately 4000 m²": "约4 000平方米",
  "Approximately 2000 m²": "约2000平方米",
  "Approximately 3464 m²": "约3464平方米",
  "Area of triangle = ½|A × B| = ½|A||B|sinθ = ½(100)(80)sin60° = ½(100)(80)(0.866) = 3464 m².": "三角形区域 = 1⁄2 A × B = 1⁄2 A B sin = 1⁄2 100 (80)sin60° = 1⁄2 100 (80) (0.866) = 3464 m2。",
  "A boat aims to cross a 200 m wide river flowing east at 3 m/s. The boat can travel at 5 m/s in still water. If the boat aims upstream at angle θ to go straight across, what angle and crossing time are needed?": "一艘船旨在以3米/秒向东行驶200米宽的河流。该船在静水中可以以5米/秒的速度行驶。如果该船的上游方向是角直行,那么需要什么角度和穿越时间?",
  "θ ≈ 30° upstream, t = 46 s": "* 30度上游,t=46秒",
  "θ ≈ 53° upstream, t = 40 s": "53度上游,t=40度",
  "θ ≈ 45° upstream, t = 57 s": "45度上游,t=57秒",
  "θ ≈ 37° upstream, t = 50 s": "37度上游,t=50度",
  "To go straight: 5sinθ = 3, sinθ = 0.6, θ ≈ 37°. Crossing speed = 5cosθ = 5(0.8) = 4 m/s. Time = 200/4 = 50 s.": "直线: 5sin = 3, sin = 0.6,   37°. 交叉速度 = 5cos = 5(0.8) = 4m/s. 时间 = 200/4 = 50s.",
  "An engineer needs to verify that a support beam is perpendicular to a wall. The beam direction is represented by vector A = (2, 3, -1) and the wall normal by B = (1, -1, -1). Are they perpendicular?": "工程师需要核实支持光束是否与墙垂直。 光束方向由矢量 A = (2, 3, - 1) 表示, 而墙的正常度由 B = (1, 1, 1 - 1) 表示, 它们是否垂直?",
  "Yes, because A·B = 0": "是,因为AAB=0",
  "No, because A·B = -2, not zero": "否,因为AAB= -2,不是零",
  "No, because A·B = 0, which means they are perpendicular to each other, not the beam perpendicular to wall": "否,因为AAB=0,这意味着它们相互垂直,而不是横梁与墙垂直。",
  "Yes, because the cross product is zero": "是的,因为交叉产品为零",
  "A·B = (2)(1) + (3)(-1) + (-1)(-1) = 2 - 3 + 1 = 0. Actually A·B = 0, so they ARE perpendicular. The beam direction is perpendicular to the wall normal, meaning it lies in the plane of the wall.": "AB=(2)(1)+(3)-1+((3)-1)+(-1)+(-1)=2-3+1=0。实际上,AB=0,因此它们是垂直的。光束方向与墙的正常相垂直,意思是它位于墙的平面上。",
  "A crane lifts a load using three cables. Cable tensions are T₁ = 500 N at 30° from vertical in the east-west plane, T₂ = 500 N at 30° from vertical in the north-south plane, and the load weighs 1000 N. Is the system in equilibrium?": "一台起重机用三条电缆卸载负载。 电缆紧张度为:从东-西平面的垂直高度起T1 = 30°时为500牛顿,从北-南平面的垂直起T2 = 500牛顿,负重为1000牛顿。 系统平衡吗?",
  "No, the horizontal components don't cancel": "不, 水平组件不会取消",
  "Yes, the tensions balance the weight perfectly": "是的,紧张状态完全平衡了重量",
  "Yes, because 500 + 500 = 1000 N": "是,因为500+500=1000N",
  "No, the vertical components only sum to 866 N, less than the 1000 N weight": "否,垂直部件仅等于866牛顿,低于1000牛顿重量",
  "Vertical components: T₁cos30° + T₂cos30° = 500(0.866) + 500(0.866) = 866 N, which is less than the 1000 N weight. The system is not in equilibrium.": "垂直组件:T1cos30°+T2cos30°=500(0.866)+500(0.866)+500(0.866)=866N,低于1000N重量。系统不平衡。",
  "A GPS system reports a hiker's displacement as 3 km east, then 4 km north, then 1 km vertically up a mountain. What is the straight-line distance from the starting point?": "据全球定位系统报告,徒步旅行者流离失所的东面为3公里,北面为4公里,然后垂直上山1公里。 距离起点直线距离是多少?",
  "sqrt(24) ≈ 4.90 km": "Sqrt(24)  4.90公里",
  "5 km": "5公里 5公里",
  "8 km": "8公里",
  "sqrt(26) ≈ 5.10 km": "sqrt( 26)  5. 10公里",
  "3D displacement magnitude = sqrt(3² + 4² + 1²) = sqrt(9 + 16 + 1) = sqrt(26) ≈ 5.10 km.": "3D 流离失所规模 = sqrt(32+42+12) = sqrt(9+16+1) = sqrt(26) = 5.10公里。",
  "A robotic arm applies a force F = (4, -3, 2) N at a point with position vector r = (1, 2, -1) m from the pivot. What is the torque about the pivot?": "机器人臂在矢量 r = (1, 2, - 1) m 的方位点上应用F = (4, 3, 3, 2) N 力。 枢轴的法力是什么?",
